songs.title: Boy Bye
songs.lyrics:
Boy I ain’t got time for you
Too much on my plate
Boy, I can’t make my mind up for you
Way too much to say

(Pre Chorus)
Oh, I love it when your mad
But hate when you’re sad
Because I won’t be glad if it’s that bad

(Chorus)
Boy, boy, boy, I need you outta my life
No, no, no, outta my sight
I am leaving without you tonight
So don’t cry, boy bye
Boy, boy, boy, I need you outta my life
No, no, no, outta my sight
I am leaving without you tonight
It’s alright, boy bye

See them other girls
They can have the world
I could have my space just like them
But after all this time, baby I won’t lie
Please I’d rather die, Oh

(Pre Chorus)
Oh, I love it when your mad
But hate when you’re sad
Because I won’t be glad if it’s that bad

(Chorus)
Boy, boy, boy, I need you outta my life
No, no, no, outta my sight
I am leaving without you tonight
So don’t cry, boy bye
Boy, boy, boy, I need you outta my life
No, no, no, outta my sight
I am leaving without you tonight
It’s alright, boy bye
